   <marc21:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="520">
      <marc21:subfield code="a">Button writes with updates on movies and other arts and culture he has seen in New York, the activities of mutual friends, giving Marlon Brando a tour of MoMA,  and planning for a trip to visit Fabian in California. &lt;br&gt;Year based on Button's mentions of the "new movie" &lt;em&gt;Some like it hot&lt;/em&gt; and Eileen Farrell performing as Ariadne with the San Francisco opera. &lt;br&gt;Portions of the letter are handwritten and portions are typewritten, cut out and pasted onto the handwritten sheet.</marc21:subfield>
